{"tid":113992,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(((天氣涷先來走雀)))有朋友走失左隻雀仔！！跪求眾巴絲幫幫手留意","createTime":"2017-02-09T12:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T03:37:09.000Z","uid":8120,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"737ad158556a5a1015cbd845d9e864ec8767aba8","tid":113992,"uid":8120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:11:46.000Z","msg":"連登有愛！！！！！！<br />\n//今日大概10:15 <br />\n第一次落街曬雀 趁我換糧時偷走左出來 我試過引佢返來 <br />\n但又抓唔到佢<br />\n樓下公園d人話唔見波波 <br />\n希望佢係飛左去好心人既屋企<br />\n華富上村華景樓高層 <br />\n走失左一隻黃色桃面lovebird <br />\n兩個月大 接近麻雀size<br />\n驚人，識飛 但唔係好識降落，佢個名叫波波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到的話 盡可能幫我抓佢入籠先<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢幾日好凍</span> </span>所以最好都有人收留住佢先<br />\n紙箱+抹手紙墊底 最好加暖包痴係其中一邊 淨係比水就得<br />\n抓到時最好儘快聯絡我 我會仆去接返佢<br />\n如尋獲 請致電/ whatsapp <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">61495100</span> </span>有薄酬//<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a1o4cins\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa1o4cins&h=aafd7f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x36s9i8p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx36s9i8p&h=a4594a98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"193567c8ab53973eb06c4efcb767beacb6b740df","tid":113992,"uid":8120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376e649c4996518e465e78ec5d91b26de68b8e04","tid":113992,"uid":8120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67972cddf245b55f5368fd74991b5a6aa282f95f","tid":113992,"uid":8120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eaa7c683f9fa90d849575906e3399583b60e51d","tid":113992,"uid":9677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,